- merge descriptors keep merge policy and lineage metadata in persisted engine state
- merge replay can inherit an optional merge-base prefix without rewriting parent histories

The `engine::tests::merge_creation_records_parent_heads_and_metadata` test verifies parent-head preservation, merge policy metadata, and merge-base replay behavior.
